reviews.review_text: a phil night i got on the bus in aug 31 /81 at the aladin las wages heard moring dew   when the cirus came to irvine it was a good time   i still dident know who lead the band  on althea phil takes over thout it was jerry song  this is a fine reason it on  PHIL ZONE the mix on this hit the spot i went to this show trying to remember      there  was a dancing bear in the parking lot  giving away does took one in the eye  it was on good ring  and you can still tell
